reviewText: It could have been longer and it should have had newer episodes.  I like watching it and I really like Johnny Test.

Same old stuff.  Can't understand why a cartoon that has been running since 2005 can't seem to release any more original shows than seasons 1 & 2.  Very disappointed.  I would have given it "no stars" but that wasn't an option.
I have tv's in my vehicle and this is perfect for long road trips. My children really enjoy Johnny Test!
received by the estimated delivery date.  i was disappointed with the fact that it was a repeat of some of the episodes that i bought on the complete seasons 1-4
